    parentName: "ol"
  }, "Time #2 correctly.")), mdx("p", null, "Now, I don't think this is earth shattering information, but to ", mdx("em", {
    parentName: "p"
  }, "internalize"), " it was a big deal. At Google, #2 can feel tough because no one is telling you what to get involved in. There's a million potential projects that you ", mdx("em", {
    parentName: "p"
